<br>
I have known people who destroyed their lives because of addiction to drugs and alcohol and, let me tell you something, if you want to compare eating, shopping or Everquest with the nightmare that is true, chemical, addiction, you are tragically naive.<br>
<br>
This new-age BS pseudo psychology crap is just another example of how ridiculous our culture is becoming.  Labeling what amounts to nothing more than extreme immaturity and a lack of self-control as an &quot;addiction&quot; does everyone a disservice because it provides people with a crutch and a rationalization for their self-destructive behavior.<br>
<br>
